title: WHIRLING / Kim barks
description: Kim tells you he has a menu for questions after he's in the team.

dialogueTree.title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""If you have more questions, don't..."
dialogueTree.english: "If you have more questions, don't hesitate to ask."
dialogueTree.polish: „Gdybyś miał jeszcze jakieś pytania, to nie krępuj się”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Калі ў цябе будуць яшчэ якія-небудзь пытанні, не саромейся».
